-- Galaxy Macau's Chief Operating Officer Wolstenholme, Marketing Chief QuitR
-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 2010-10-25T14:20:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-25/galaxy-macau-s-chief-operating-officer-wolstenholme-marketing-chief-quitr.html
Galaxy Entertainment Group Ltd . said
 Steve Wolstenholme , chief operating officer of Galaxy Macau, has
resigned for personal reasons, and  Michael Mecca , COO of the
parent, will take the job “in the interim.”  Jeffrey King , senior vice president of marketing at Galaxy
Macau, has resigned and  Raymond Yap , the head of international
premium market development at the parent, will fill in until a
permanent replacement is found, Galaxy said in a press release
posted on its website today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  